Since our opening we’ve been able to expand our menu, turn visitors into loyal customers, and give back to the community via food drives and fundraisers. We’ve also participated in many events and been given some awards along the way. Here are a few:
  • Restaurant Week 2015 Best New Classical
  • Top 10 New Local Joints
  • Best Happy Hour on Main St
  • Top 25 Hot Wings In The City
  • Best Sundaes for Sunday
